Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Candidates claim victory in TV debate
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w4tz
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 28 Sep 1980
Polls will chart Carter's performance in TV debate while the other two candidates both claim victory. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less